extends layout.pug

block content

  article.portfolio-intro
 
    h1 Hello, my name's John!

    p Glad you're here! This portfolio demonstrates my skills with various web technologies and is meant to generate discussion about how I can help your company. For starters, here are some projects I've put together while learning JavaScript. 


  article.portfolio-project-thumbs
    .projects-box.box.grid

      each item in projects   

        .cell
          a(href=`/projects/${item.id}`)
            img.thumbnail(src=`${item.image_urls[0]}.png`, alt=`${item.image_alt}`)
            h6= item.project_name

